title: SV Elversberg vs FC Heidenheim 1846 - Bundesliga 2024/25 Play-Offs
description: The German Bundesliga is live and exclusive only on beIN. The 2024–25 Bundesliga will be the 62nd season of the Bundesliga. The league comprises of 18 teams 16 of which competed in the league campaign during the previous season, while the remaining two were promoted from Bundesliga 2.

title: Eintracht Braunschweig vs FC Saarbrucken - Bundesliga 2 - 2024/25 Play-Offs
description: Bundesliga 2 division is the mens second professional association football division of the German football league system. Bundesliga 2 is the ideal proving ground for younger players in Germany before stepping up to the Bundesliga, but it’s also simply a great league to watch if you want drama and excitement at a level that still boasts quality.

title: Stuttgart vs Mainz 05 - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 2
description: Anrie Chase came off the bench to make his Bundesliga debut for VfB Stuttgart on matchday 1 and become the seventh Japanese player in their Bundesliga history, the most of any club. Chase completed all 20 passes he attempted – the most of any player that had a 100% success rate on matchday 1. Nadiem Amiri scored Mainz’s first goal of the new Bundesliga season on matchday 1 – the second direct free-kick he’s scored in 2024, a feat no other player has managed this year. Since Amiri’s move to Mainz at the end of January 2024, only Kevin Stoger has had a hand in more shots than him.

title: Eintracht Frankfurt vs Hoffenheim - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 2
description: Only 10 players in Bundesliga history have ever scored at least three goals in two consecutive games. Hoffenheim’s Andrej Kramaric is the first player to achieve this twice. No player has ever done it in three straight games in Bundesliga history. Andrej Kramaric has become the first Hoffenheim player to have a hand in at least one goal in eight consecutive Bundesliga games. Since the start of April, no player in the league has contributed to as many goals. His hat-trick against Kiel means he tops the league’s scoring charts for the fourth time in his career.

title: Bayer Leverkusen vs RB Leipzig - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 2
description: Leipzigs Willi Orban is suspended for this fixture after being sent off against VfL Bochum – it was the third red card of his Bundesliga career, the most of any RBL player. Leipzig have failed to win any of their last four top-flight matches without their captain in the starting line-up, conceding 10 goals in the process. Summer signing Antonio Nusa became the third-youngest player to score a Bundesliga goal for Leipzig with his winner against Bochum last time. Only Hugo Novoa and Dayot Upamecano found the back of the net at a younger age for RBL in the division. Nusa is also the first RBL player to score on both his Bundesliga and DFB-Pokal debuts.

title: Heidenheim vs Augsburg - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 2
description: Heidenheims Jan Schoppner scored his third Bundesliga goal on what was his 27th appearance in the division last time out – each of his three goals have come following a set piece. Hes now scored more goals in 27 top-flight games than in 81 second-division appearances. Augsburgs Samuel Essende scored to put his side 2-1 up on his Bundesliga debut against SV Werder Bremen last weekend. Hes the fifth player to find the back of the net on his top-flight debut for FCA, with Sven Michel most recently managing the feat last season. The Congolese striker is also the first Augsburg player to score on both his Bundesliga and DFB-Pokal debuts.

title: Frankfurt vs Hoffenheim - Mini Match - Bundesliga 2024/25
description: Frankfurt vs Hoffenheim - Extended Highlights - Bundesliga 2024/25

title: Bayern Munchen vs Freiburg - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 2
description: Freiburgs Lucas Holer has scored more goals in all competitions against FC Bayern than he has against any other side. The last time these two sides met in March, Holer scored the final goal in a 2-2 draw. Among current Bundesliga players, only Hoffenheims Andrej Kramaric has netted more goals against FCB. Julian Schuster is the second head coach to win his first Bundesliga game with SC Freiburg – no coach has ever managed to win their first two matches at SC. Schuster took just one point from 11 Bundesliga games against FCB as a player, coming in a 1-1 home draw in August 2013.

title: Holstein Kiel vs Wolfsburg - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 2
description: Wolfsburgs Lovro Majer scored the second brace of his Bundesliga career on his 33rd appearance in the division last time out. Six of his last seven Bundesliga goal contributions have come at home. Only SV Darmstadt had a lower xG last season than VfL Wolfsburg. Both Kiel and Wolfsburg generated an xG of 1.9 on the opening matchday this term – only Leverkusen, Bayern, Hoffenheim and Freiburg were better off in this regard.

description: DTM. Three letters encapsulating motorsport tradition like few other racing series. Born in 1984, the DTM is coming off one of its strongest ever seasons under the guidance of the ADAC! Supported by a comprehensive support package including the ADAC GT Masters and ADAC GT4 Germany – the DTM package combines heritage with a powerful drive and a glittering future!

This will be the seventh season of the championship and the fifth after a merger with Formula Renault Eurocup which resulted in the change of the engine supplier to Alpine.

description: The 2024/25 UEFA Champions League Final, featuring Paris Saint-Germain (PSG) and Inter Milan, is set to take place on Saturday, 31 May 2025, at the Allianz Arena in Munich, Germany. This match marks the first-ever European encounter between these two clubs. This final is particularly noteworthy as PSG aims to secure their first-ever Champions League title, while Inter seeks their fourth, having last won in 2010.

The event takes place from May 25 to June 8, 2025. This iconic clay-court championship features top players from around the world competing for glory in singles, doubles, and mixed doubles categories. As always, Roland Garros promises intense competition and unforgettable moments in the world of tennis.

title: Nantes vs Cesson - LNH Division 1 - French Handball Starligue
description: Dive into the excitement of French handball with Liqui Moly Starligue, formerly LNH Division 1. Established in 1952, this premier league event features 16 top teams battling for glory. Champions earn spots in the EHF Champions League, while cup winners qualify for the European League.

description: Welcome to the 4th episode of Inside Sailing for 2025 - the TV program which brings you all the very best action from some of the most spectacular sailing events around the world. Through this epic sport we discover new horizons, new challenges, exciting journeys and some breathtaking sceneries.

title: World Sailing Show 2025
description: The World Sailing Show 2025 brings you the most thrilling moments from elite sailing competitions around the globe. From high-speed foiling action to tactical offshore battles, this episode covers top events like the America’s Cup, SailGP, and The Ocean Race. Meet the world’s best sailors, explore cutting-edge boat technology, and witness the drama of high-stakes racing on the water.
